Package org.batfish.common.bdd

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BDDInteger  
    BDDIpSpaceSpecializer
    An IpSpaceSpecializer that uses a BDD to represent the headerspace to which we want to specialize.
    BDDOps  
    BDDPacket
    A collection of attributes describing an packet, represented using BDDs
    BDDSourceManager
    Manages BDD variables to track a packet's source: which interface it entered the node through, if any.
    BDDUtils
    Various utility methods for working with BDDs.
    HeaderSpaceToBDD
    Convert a headerspace constraint to a BDD.
    IpAccessListToBDD
    Converts IpAccessLists or AclLineMatchExprs to BDD.
    IpSpaceToBDD
    Visitor that converts an IpSpace to a BDD.
    MemoizedIpAccessListToBDD
    An AclLineMatchExprToBDD that memoizes its AclLineMatchExprToBDD#visit method using an IdentityHashMap.
    MemoizedIpSpaceToBDD
    An IpSpaceToBDD that memoizes its GenericIpSpaceVisitor.visit(org.batfish.datamodel.IpSpace) method using an IdentityHashMap.
